OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,FA police force described by its own
OL,7,Fchief constable as "institutionally
OL,8,Fracist" has introduced new stop and
OL,9,Fsearch procedures.
OL,11,FChief Constable Sarah Crew criticised
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police in July 2023
OL,13,Fafter a report into the organisation.
OL,15,FSince then, the force's own figures
OL,16,Fshow that stop and search rates have
OL,17,Factually risen for black people.
