OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,FThe latest rates show black people are
OL,7,Fnow 6.77 times more likely to be
OL,8,Fstopped and searched compared with
OL,9,F5.63 times in 2022.
OL,11,FThe force has paid for a film showing
OL,12,Fthe dos and don't of stop and search -
OL,13,Fmade by teenagers at production firm
OL,14,Fin St Pauls.
OL,16,FIt has also introduced new measures,
OL,17,Fincluding:
