OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,FChief Constable Sarah Crew said: "When
OL,7,FI made the statement on institutional
OL,8,Fracism, I said I would come back in
OL,9,Fone year to update on the progress we
OL,10,Fhave made, to back my words with
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,F"The report we are publishing
OL,14,Fdocuments the activity that has taken
OL,15,Fplace since then and, importantly,
OL,16,Fsets out how we will continue our
OL,17,Fprogress in becoming a truly anti-
OL,18,Fracist organisation; maintaining
OL,19,Fmomentum to improve trust and
OL,20,Fconfidence in communities where it is
OL,21,Fmost needed.
OL,26,@nD@bOUuD@AOU
