OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,F"Had I not acknowledged that
OL,7,Finstitutional racism exists in the
OL,8,Forganisation, I'm sure the work we are
OL,9,Fdoing in this area would not have been
OL,10,Fsuccessful ` the communities most
OL,11,Fdirectly affected by it would not
OL,12,Ftrust us, work with us or take us at
OL,13,Four word.
OL,15,F"Without trust there is no consent,
OL,16,Fand without consent we no longer have
OL,17,Flegitimacy to police. It is this
OL,18,Fsimple. It is fundamental.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
