OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,F"In the past year over 70 people have
OL,7,Fjoined our Race Matters Community
OL,8,FNetwork, to help us shape anti-racist
OL,9,Fpolicing in Avon and Somerset.
OL,11,F"I'm so grateful to all those people,
OL,12,Fwhose input and voices are central to
OL,13,Fthe changes we are making."
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset is one of only three
OL,16,Fforces in the country to declare
OL,17,Fitself "institutionally racist" - the
OL,18,Fothers are Police Scotland and British
OL,19,FTransport Police.
