OL,3,CNew stop and search procedures for
OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police, West Midland
OL,7,Fand Greater Manchester forces have
OL,8,Frefused to do so.
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset's Police Federation
OL,11,Fhad reservations about the way Sarah
OL,12,FCrew made her announcement last year.
OL,14,FIain Prideaux, the Acting Chairmen of
OL,15,Fthe Police Federation's Avon &
OL,16,FSomerset Branch said: "Officers heard
OL,17,Fthey were racist, so it became
OL,18,Fpersonal. We don't make a product,
OL,19,Fwe're a service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
