OL,4,C'institutionally racist' police force
OL,6,F"We work with a community. And having
OL,7,Ftrust and confidence from the
OL,8,Fcommunity is incredibly important.
OL,10,F"We needed to understand where the
OL,11,FChief was coming from in making that
OL,12,Fdeclaration. And since then we're
OL,13,Fbeginning to understand it was about
OL,14,Fthe processes."
